428
00:26:44,060 --> 00:26:46,563
Ma'am, let me take you home.

429
00:26:47,314 --> 00:26:50,483
No, it's okay.
I can't just leave him here.

430
00:26:50,609 --> 00:26:53,320
He's lying in the cold all by himself.

431
00:26:53,903 --> 00:26:56,197
He doesn't even have any parents.

432
00:26:56,323 --> 00:26:58,700
