00:28:00,512 --> 00:28:01,596
Ma'am.

448
00:28:05,266 --> 00:28:07,811
Ma'am. Ma'am, wake up.

449
00:28:09,813 --> 00:28:11,481
When can we check out the scene?

450
00:28:11,564 --> 00:28:14,067
The police are still investigating,
so not yet.

451
00:28:14,150 --> 00:28:15,944
They won't give us
any information.

452
00:28:16,027 --> 00:28:18,571
I think Joojin Constructions' Legal Team
is on the move.

453
00:28:22,158 --> 00:28:24,035
Who made the report?

454
00:28:24,953 --> 00:28:26,538
-Mr. Kim Sang-cheol?
-Yes?

455
00:28:26,913 --> 00:28:29,624
Yes... Yes, I made the report.

456
00:28:29,708 --> 00:28:32,085
What kind of condition was Mr. Yu in?

457
00:28:32,168 --> 00:28:35,213
His body was tied to the conveyor belt,
