458
00:28:35,296 --> 00:28:37,048
So I called 911.

459
00:28:37,132 --> 00:28:39,968
Was the emergency stop switch turned on?

460
00:28:40,051 --> 00:28:42,887
He had a few drinks before working,
so he must've forgotten.

461
00:28:42,971 --> 00:28:45,056
How much did Mr. Yu drink?

462
00:28:45,140 --> 00:28:48,476
Our team went for dinner,
so I think he had

