to a different hospital?

472
00:29:17,297 --> 00:29:19,299
He couldn't get the surgery
he needed there,

473
00:29:19,382 --> 00:29:20,633
so he was brought here.

474
00:29:20,717 --> 00:29:23,261
What time did he arrive?
Was he conscious up until then?

475
00:29:24,929 --> 00:29:27,182
