00:29:56,544 --> 00:29:58,963
Please call us if you have any questions.

489
00:29:59,047 --> 00:30:00,548
We'll do our best to answer them.

490
00:30:05,011 --> 00:30:07,931
Don't meet anyone, and don't say anything.

491
00:30:08,014 --> 00:30:09,599
We'll take care of this.

492
00:30:10,183 --> 00:30:12,602
-Yes, of course. You heard that, right?
-Yes.

493
00:30:30,203 --> 00:30:31,329
