494
00:30:32,622 --> 00:30:34,123
She passed out.

495
00:30:34,207 --> 00:30:37,460
She's been crying all day
and hasn't had anything to eat.

496
00:30:39,212 --> 00:30:40,630
Are there other family members?

497
00:30:41,381 --> 00:30:42,382
