due to an industrial accident.

502
00:30:59,983 --> 00:31:01,860
That's when I studied a lot about it.

503
00:31:03,945 --> 00:31:06,865
My goodness, it must've been very hard.

504
00:31:08,324 --> 00:31:11,953
It wasn't so hard
because someone helped us back then.

505
00:31:38,062 --> 00:31:39,105
Ms. Kang.

506
00:31:40,398 --> 00:31:42,358
I got a call from the mayor's office.

507
00:31:42,442 --> 00:31:43,610
He wants to meet today.

508
00:31:47,405 --> 00:31:49,449
LONE-PARENT PROJECT PROPOSAL FOR JUNGIL-GU

509
00:31:53,244 --> 00:31:54,621
What are you planning to do?

510
00:31:54,704 --> 00:31:57,582
I should look thoroughly into
how the accident occurred.

511
00:31:57,665 --> 00:32:00,335
A man just died,
and they asked her to sign an agreement.

512
00:32:00,752 --> 00:32:03,588
I'll do everything I can to make them
beg for forgiveness.

513
00:32:03,671 --> 00:32:04,714
Just drop it.

514
00:32:05,882 --> 00:32:07,717
The accident happened in your district,

515
00:32:07,800 --> 00:32:10,762
but they're residents of our district.
I'll take care of it.

516
00:32:14,098 --> 00:32:15,308
What will you do?

517
00:32:15,391 --> 00:32:18,061
I’ll make sure the funeral procedure
and the compensation--

518
00:32:18,144 --> 00:32:19,812
I can't believe you're saying that!

519
00:32:21,189 --> 00:32:23,316
I also feel sorry about what happened.

520
00:32:23,399 --> 00:32:25,234
Are you here to console his family

521
00:32:25,318 --> 00:32:26,986
or because of Lee Chang-jin?

522
00:32:32,951 --> 00:32:34,327
My gosh.

523
00:32:38,122 --> 00:32:41,417
If you're here because of the latter,
you shouldn't get involved

524
00:32:41,501 --> 00:32:43,086
before I get disappointed in you.

525
00:32:54,847 --> 00:32:55,848
Tae-jun.

526
00:33:00,603 --> 00:33:03,356
Don't get intoxicated
with what Mr. Lee has to offer.

527
00:33:18,830 --> 00:33:19,998
MR. LEE CHANG-JIN

528
00:33:26,129 --> 00:33:27,296
Hi, this is Jang Tae-jun.

529
00:33:28,923 --> 00:33:32,969
Mr. Jang, didn't I ask you
to take care of the situation?

530
00:33:33,052 --> 00:33:35,805
Why is an intern
from your office going around

531
00:33:35,888 --> 00:33:37,640
asking unnecessary questions?

532
00:33:37,724 --> 00:33:39,726
You should keep an eye on
your subordinates.

533
00:33:39,809 --> 00:33:42,437
Do I really need to call you
regarding stuff like this?

534
00:33:45,398 --> 00:33:48,109
-I'm sorry.
-Please take better care of the situation.

535
00:33:48,192 --> 00:33:49,610
Think carefully about who it is

536
00:33:49,694 --> 00:33:53,781
that's going to make you
an assemblyman before you do anything.

537
00:34:06,335 --> 00:34:09,005
MR. LEE CHANG-JIN

538
00:34:33,488 --> 00:34:36,074
-I heard you know her.
-I do.

539
00:34:36,949 --> 00:34:39,952
I met her while I was promoting
the public hearing at the market.

540
00:34:40,078 --> 00:34:41,579
She was at the hearing, too.

541
00:34:41,829 --> 00:34:43,581
-She was there?
-Yes.

542
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:48,836
She used to sell things at the market
with her grandson.

543
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:51,756
But they got kicked out
due to the redevelopment.

544
00:34:52,340 --> 00:34:55,551
I heard that's why her grandson
began working at the factory.

545
00:35:04,727 --> 00:35:07,396
I heard that you are a competent man.

546
00:35:07,688 --> 00:35:11,818
Please help me so that
I can keep doing business at the market

547
00:35:11,901 --> 00:35:13,361
with my grandson.

548
00:35:14,237 --> 00:35:16,197
I ask of you, sir.

549
00:35:17,281 --> 00:35:18,533
Please help us out.

550
00:35:18,616 --> 00:35:21,410
I ask of you. Please.

551
00:35:39,303 --> 00:35:41,347
LONE-PARENT PROJECT PROPOSAL FOR JUNGIL-GU

552
00:35:49,689 --> 00:35:51,774
I'm not sure if it's okay for me
to take this.

553
00:35:51,858 --> 00:35:53,985
All you need to do is make a decision.

554
00:35:54,694 --> 00:35:56,112
Yes, I know.

555
00:35:57,071 --> 00:35:59,532
But it's not something
I can decide on my own.

556
00:36:25,391 --> 00:36:26,809
What brings you here?

557
00:36:26,893 --> 00:36:28,769
We haven't been on great terms recently.

558
00:36:28,853 --> 00:36:30,688
So I came to see you.

559
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:32,148
How about a drink?

560
00:36:32,231 --> 00:36:34,525
We're not close enough
to have drinks together.

561
00:36:35,610 --> 00:36:37,278
I'll be off now.

562
00:36:37,778 --> 00:36:40,740
Are you just going to give up on
Jungil-gu like this?

563
00:36:41,574 --> 00:36:43,868
Why do you keep choosing the hard way?

564
00:36:46,412 --> 00:36:49,582
You can't just give away
what you've been working so hard on.

565
00:36:53,836 --> 00:36:56,797
I want you to be in charge.
The mayor will help you out.

566
00:36:56,881 --> 00:36:58,966
You've been working for me
for a long time.

567
00:36:59,050 --> 00:37:00,301
I don't want to stop you.

568
00:37:01,719 --> 00:37:04,639
I'm sure you're not doing me a favor
with no strings attached.

569
00:37:04,889 --> 00:37:07,350
-What do you want?
-There's only one thing I want.

570
00:37:08,392 --> 00:37:09,518
Jang Tae-jun.

571
00:37:18,778 --> 00:37:21,030
We should've dealt with him
from the start.

572
00:37:21,113 --> 00:37:22,865
The reason Mr. Song
has come this far

573
00:37:22,949 --> 00:37:26,202
and the reason our relationship
became so bad is all because of him.

574
00:37:50,309 --> 00:37:52,728
How's his grandmother?

575
00:37:54,939 --> 00:37:58,317
She was just out of energy.
Everything else is fine.

576
00:37:58,401 --> 00:37:59,568
I'm relieved.

577
00:38:06,659 --> 00:38:09,787
You're here to tell me something,
aren't you?

578
00:38:11,122 --> 00:38:11,998
Jin-su...

579
00:38:13,165 --> 00:38:14,625
Jin-su was a good guy.

580
00:38:14,709 --> 00:38:16,877
He always said he's going to save up

581
00:38:17,420 --> 00:38:19,130
to open a store for his grandmother.

582
00:38:29,015 --> 00:38:30,766
It's the CCTV footage of the accident.

583
00:38:31,684 --> 00:38:34,020
I copied the footage
before the company deleted it.

584
00:38:45,656 --> 00:38:47,783
Here’s the list of the stockholders.

585
00:38:47,867 --> 00:38:50,286
Three construction firms are
in the redevelopment

586
00:38:50,369 --> 00:38:52,788
along with over 20 subcontractors.

587
00:38:52,872 --> 00:38:56,167
The subcontractors are unlisted,
so I couldn't see their stockholders.

588
00:38:56,250 --> 00:38:58,794
But I found something peculiar
while looking into this.

589
00:38:58,878 --> 00:39:02,840
-What did you find?
-This is a list of all the subcontractors.

590
00:39:04,425 --> 00:39:07,636
The subcontractors of Joojin Constructions

591
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:10,806
are all located in districts
that are run by people you know.

592
00:39:10,890 --> 00:39:12,683
UIGWANG CITY, SEONGJIN CITY REDEVELOPMENT
SUBCONTRACTORS

593
00:39:12,767 --> 00:39:15,519
Jungbu City, Chairperson Lee.

594
00:39:16,020 --> 00:39:18,898
Gwanghyeon City, Mr. Ahn.

595
00:39:18,981 --> 00:39:21,233
Jingyeong City, Mr. No.

596
00:39:22,401 --> 00:39:24,737
Mr. Song, if the redevelopment
is canceled,

597
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:26,405
I won't be the only one affected.

598
00:39:28,866 --> 00:39:30,451
If things don't go well,

599
00:39:30,534 --> 00:39:32,745
you might also end up getting in trouble.

600
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:35,456
Mr. Jang.

601
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,793
You need to see this.

602
00:40:04,735 --> 00:40:06,529
Mr. Yu wasn't intoxicated.

603
00:40:06,612 --> 00:40:08,364
He turned on
the emergency stop switch.

604
00:40:08,447 --> 00:40:11,242
The conveyor belt was the problem.

605
00:40:11,784 --> 00:40:15,204
And Mr. Kim Sang-cheol called 911
as soon as he came to the factory

606
00:40:15,287 --> 00:40:16,455
and saw what happened.

607
00:40:18,165 --> 00:40:20,501
But the manager called 911 again
and said he's fine.

608
00:40:20,584 --> 00:40:23,754
He sent back the ambulance and took
Mr. Yu to the designated hospital.

609
00:40:25,714 --> 00:40:28,592
Designated hospitals can hide
industrial accidents.

610
00:40:29,176 --> 00:40:32,847
That place is an hour away
from the general hospital in Uigwang City.

611
00:40:32,930 --> 00:40:35,433
He could've lived if he was taken there.

612
00:40:35,516 --> 00:40:37,518
They practically killed him!

613
00:40:44,150 --> 00:40:46,110
Is there anyone else who knows

614
00:40:47,903 --> 00:40:49,530
that you have this flash drive?

615
00:40:50,823 --> 00:40:53,325
No, I came to see you
as soon as I received it.

616
00:41:16,182 --> 00:41:18,434
Are you here to console
his family or

617
00:41:18,517 --> 00:41:19,768
because of Lee Chang-jin?

618
00:41:25,691 --> 00:41:27,359
If Mr. Lee gets in trouble,

619
00:41:27,443 --> 00:41:29,361
it'll quickly affect us as well.

620
00:41:29,445 --> 00:41:32,198
Though I don't want to,
I have to take care of it for him.

621
00:41:41,582 --> 00:41:44,293
If you're here because of the latter,
don't get involved

622
00:41:44,376 --> 00:41:45,961
before I get disappointed in you.

623
00:41:52,635 --> 00:41:55,888
I'll help you to the best of my ability
so that you can wear

624
00:41:55,971 --> 00:41:58,057
the assemblyman badge on your chest soon.

625
00:42:19,411 --> 00:42:20,996
Are you just going to give up on

626
00:42:21,080 --> 00:42:22,540
Jungil-gu like this?

627
00:42:26,043 --> 00:42:27,753
There's only one thing I want.

628
00:42:27,836 --> 00:42:29,004
Jang Tae-jun.

629
00:42:47,439 --> 00:42:50,442
-You should come visit.
-Sure, I will.

630
00:42:51,318 --> 00:42:52,861
You must still be contemplating.

631
00:42:53,737 --> 00:42:56,240
Don't consider the seller
when you buy something.

632
00:42:56,323 --> 00:42:59,326
If it's good enough, you should buy it
even if you don't like them.

633
00:43:00,119 --> 00:43:01,954
My goodness, look who's here.

634
00:43:02,037 --> 00:43:03,622
-Mr. Mun.
-Yes, sir.

635
00:43:03,706 --> 00:43:06,250
My gosh, it's been so long.
My goodness, look at you.

636
00:43:06,333 --> 00:43:08,877
If you keep hesitating,
you'll lose it to someone else.

637
00:43:15,718 --> 00:43:16,969
Yes, of course.

638
00:43:18,053 --> 00:43:19,054
Great.

639
00:43:46,540 --> 00:43:47,374
Are you okay?

640
00:43:47,458 --> 00:43:50,294
Did you stay here all night?

641
00:43:50,377 --> 00:43:52,171
Sleeping here like this will ruin you.

642
00:43:52,254 --> 00:43:53,714
You should go home.

643
00:43:54,298 --> 00:43:55,341
I'm okay.

644
00:43:55,424 --> 00:43:57,968
I have really good stamina.

645
00:44:04,141 --> 00:44:06,477
Ma'am, don't worry too much.

646
00:44:06,560 --> 00:44:09,104
Our chief of staff will help you
resolve everything

647
00:44:09,188 --> 00:44:11,065
regarding what happened to your grandson.

648
00:44:27,289 --> 00:44:28,332
Mr. Lee.

649
00:44:36,256 --> 00:44:39,677
Mr. Jang, what brings you here
so early in the morning?

650
00:44:39,760 --> 00:44:42,137
I came to give you something.

651
00:44:44,807 --> 00:44:47,893
It's the CCTV footage of the accident.

652
00:44:50,020 --> 00:44:53,732
I guess the new attorneys I hired
are very incompetent.

653
00:44:59,029 --> 00:45:00,280
This shouldn't exist.

654
00:45:01,448 --> 00:45:04,910
Mr. Jang, you really are amazing.

655
00:45:05,035 --> 00:45:06,787
How did you manage to find this?

656
00:45:16,505 --> 00:45:18,882
Anyway, thank you.

657
00:45:18,966 --> 00:45:19,883
Since you're here,

658
00:45:20,008 --> 00:45:22,845
you should join me for breakfast
if you haven't eaten yet.

659
00:45:22,928 --> 00:45:25,264
I didn't even get to
pour you a drink last time.

660
00:45:25,347 --> 00:45:26,807
Come on in.

661
00:45:33,689 --> 00:45:35,315
There's only one thing I want.

662
00:45:35,566 --> 00:45:36,692
Jang Tae-jun.

663
00:45:45,033 --> 00:45:46,034
Ms. Kang.

664
00:45:47,911 --> 00:45:49,121
You're here.

665
00:45:51,457 --> 00:45:52,833
Nothing's been decided yet.

666
00:45:52,916 --> 00:45:54,710
Is the mayor demanding more?

667
00:45:54,793 --> 00:45:57,254
No, I'm the one who hasn't decided

668
00:45:57,713 --> 00:45:59,339
what to do yet.

669
00:46:03,177 --> 00:46:04,344
-What's that?
-Right.

670
00:46:05,220 --> 00:46:06,889
I forgot to give you this yesterday.

671
00:46:07,431 --> 00:46:10,017
There's been an accident
at a factory in Seongjin City.

672
00:46:10,768 --> 00:46:11,810
CONVEYOR BELT ACCIDENT

673
00:46:11,894 --> 00:46:13,937
-It's a conveyor belt accident.
-Yes.

674
00:46:14,021 --> 00:46:16,857
It happened in a cement factory
owned by Joojin Constructions.

675
00:46:16,940 --> 00:46:19,234
Joojin Constructions?
Isn't Mr. Lee the owner?

676
00:46:19,318 --> 00:46:22,738
Yes, that's right. I think they're
trying to conceal the accident.

677
00:46:22,821 --> 00:46:24,615
So Mr. Lee is planning to form a team

678
00:46:24,698 --> 00:46:26,784
to investigate what really happened.

679
00:46:26,867 --> 00:46:29,244
And we were requested to join the team.

680
00:46:31,038 --> 00:46:34,666
Okay, I'll meet him in person
to talk about this.

681
00:46:34,750 --> 00:46:36,251
Will that be okay?

682
00:46:36,794 --> 00:46:39,463
You know Mr. Song
and Mr. Lee aren't on good terms.

683
00:46:39,546 --> 00:46:41,298
You're already in a pickle.

684
00:46:41,381 --> 00:46:44,927
If we get involved in this,
Mr. Song won't stand still.

685
00:46:45,427 --> 00:46:47,262
We should still do what we can.

686
00:46:48,055 --> 00:46:50,307
Can you get me the files
regarding the accident?

687
00:46:56,146 --> 00:46:57,564
SEONGJIN CITY REDEVELOPMENT PLAN

688
00:47:00,651 --> 00:47:02,945
CEO OF
JOOJIN CHEMICAL/JOOJIN CONSTRUCTIONS

689
00:47:07,449 --> 00:47:10,369
Mr. Lee, everything's ready
for the press conference.

690
00:47:12,204 --> 00:47:13,288
Mr. Jang.

691
00:47:14,081 --> 00:47:15,332
Assemblyman Lee's office

692
00:47:15,415 --> 00:47:18,836
is going to hold a press conference
to demand the truth behind the accident.

693
00:47:20,963 --> 00:47:22,297
Where's Mr. Song?

694
00:47:22,381 --> 00:47:23,590
He's in his office.

695
00:47:27,302 --> 00:47:30,514
Mr. Lee formed a team to
investigate the truth behind the accident

696
00:47:30,597 --> 00:47:33,267
that happened at the factory
in Seongjin City.

697
00:47:33,350 --> 00:47:35,102
This is quite an interesting thing.

698
00:47:35,185 --> 00:47:38,021
Yes. He asked us to participate
in the investigation.

699
00:47:38,105 --> 00:47:39,231
How should I respond?

700
00:47:39,314 --> 00:47:41,316
He's doing something good,
so we should help.

701
00:47:43,026 --> 00:47:45,654
This is going to be a huge headache
for Song Hui-seop.

702
00:47:49,199 --> 00:47:50,576
Mr. Lee's asking assemblymen

703
00:47:50,659 --> 00:47:53,203
to sign a petition
and join his investigation team.

704
00:47:54,246 --> 00:47:55,914
If he holds this press conference,

705
00:47:55,998 --> 00:47:57,916
it'll have an effect on your hearing.

706
00:47:58,000 --> 00:47:59,626
We need to stop him no matter what.

707
00:47:59,960 --> 00:48:01,461
How are we going to do that?

708
00:48:03,505 --> 00:48:05,465
I think we could...

709
00:48:06,675 --> 00:48:08,010
Yes.

710
00:48:08,093 --> 00:48:09,011
Hey.

711
00:48:10,262 --> 00:48:11,430
Hey.

712
00:48:11,930 --> 00:48:14,850
What were you doing until now?
How did things get this bad?

713
00:48:19,605 --> 00:48:22,065
I think Mr. Jo is up to something as well.

714
00:48:22,149 --> 00:48:24,026
With a press conference and the media's--

715
00:48:24,109 --> 00:48:25,360
Be quiet.

716
00:48:31,950 --> 00:48:34,202
You'd better silence

717
00:48:34,286 --> 00:48:36,663
Lee Seong-min at all costs.

718
00:48:36,747 --> 00:48:39,875
You can only join the Assembly
if that prick keeps his lips sealed.

719
00:48:40,667 --> 00:48:41,835
Do you realize that?

720
00:48:43,921 --> 00:48:45,213
Yes, sir. I'm aware.

721
00:48:49,134 --> 00:48:50,177
The press conference

722
00:48:51,678 --> 00:48:53,013
won't be held.

723
00:48:57,517 --> 00:48:58,602
What do you mean?

724
00:49:07,778 --> 00:49:10,155
Have you come up with a new solution?

725
00:49:10,238 --> 00:49:12,157
Are you here to meet the victim's family?

726
00:49:12,240 --> 00:49:14,034
Please make a comment, sir.

727
00:49:14,993 --> 00:49:16,620
All right, let's go.

728
00:49:19,206 --> 00:49:23,710
Let's see.
Where would be a good place to take you?

729
00:49:23,794 --> 00:49:25,420
I'll tell you where we're going.

730
00:49:26,004 --> 00:49:27,589
Do you know a good place?

731
00:49:27,673 --> 00:49:29,341
General hospital in Uigwang City.

732
00:49:30,717 --> 00:49:32,761
-What do you mean?
-Go to the hospital,

733
00:49:32,844 --> 00:49:35,597
get on your knees,
and sincerely apologize to the bereaved.

734
00:49:35,681 --> 00:49:37,265
Cooperate with the police.

735
00:49:39,351 --> 00:49:41,353
Mr. Jang Tae-jun.

736
00:49:41,436 --> 00:49:43,230
What the heck are you saying?

737
00:49:45,649 --> 00:49:47,567
Are you here to apologize to the bereaved?

738
00:49:47,651 --> 00:49:50,737
Do you think Joojin Constructions
is responsible for what happened?

739
00:49:51,989 --> 00:49:53,490
Will there be a press...

740
00:49:53,573 --> 00:49:54,741
-Do you need help?
-Yes.

741
00:49:58,870 --> 00:50:00,664
-What's going on?
-What is happening?

742
00:50:06,044 --> 00:50:07,379
What's happening?

743
00:50:08,213 --> 00:50:09,423
I'm sorry.

744
00:50:10,799 --> 00:50:14,094
The company will take care of everything.

745
00:50:15,137 --> 00:50:16,346
I give you my word, ma'am.

746
00:50:25,188 --> 00:50:28,734
For this, I think it'd be better
to go with what we discussed...

747
00:50:28,817 --> 00:50:29,818
Sir!

748
00:50:34,114 --> 00:50:35,782
Mr. Lee Chang-jin,

749
00:50:35,866 --> 00:50:39,327
the CEO of Joojin Constructions,
visited the family of Mr. Yu Jin-su,

750
00:50:39,411 --> 00:50:42,706
who lost his life in the conveyor belt
accident at the cement factory

751
00:50:42,789 --> 00:50:44,583
and apologized on his knees.

752
00:50:44,833 --> 00:50:47,544
He expressed his sincere condolences
on the death of Mr. Yu,

