occupational health and safety

1007
01:06:41,872 --> 01:06:44,542
while being actively involved
in various other activities.

1008
01:07:13,612 --> 01:07:14,864
This is my life.

1009
01:07:14,947 --> 01:07:16,240
So stop meddling!

1010
01:07:16,323 --> 01:07:18,367
It's hard coming back if you go too far.

1011
01:07:18,451 --> 01:07:19,785
Listen to me, just this once.

1012
01:07:19,869 --> 01:07:22,663
Mr. Lee is really putting up a fight
with Mr. Song this time.

1013
01:07:22,747 --> 01:07:24,749
A man who has nothing to lose

1014
01:07:24,832 --> 01:07:26,417
can be such a hassle.

1015
01:07:26,500 --> 01:07:28,878
Use this chance to destroy him
and make a comeback.

1016
01:07:29,003 --> 01:07:30,838
I know the right man for this.

1017
01:07:30,921 --> 01:07:32,339
How are you related to him?

1018
01:07:32,423 --> 01:07:34,258
If this gets disclosed Mr. Song will...

1019
01:07:34,341 --> 01:07:36,594
Are you OK losing
someone that's good at his job?

1020
01:07:36,677 --> 01:07:38,846
It's the right time to destroy him.

